# Order ticket UI (frozen)

The **New order ticket** layout and controls have fixed visual behavior (heights, backgrounds, borders, focus rings, Ant Design token wiring). **Do not modify** the areas below unless the user clearly asks to change the order ticket in the same task.

## Do not change

**`client/src/App.css`**

- Rules for `.order-entry-ticket-select` (including `.ant-select-outlined` chains)
- `.order-entry-symbol-autocomplete` and symbol typeahead dropdown
- `.order-entry-form__panel--advanced` Select overrides
- `.app-card.app-card--form .order-entry-form` blocks that style `.ant-input`, `.ant-select`, `.ant-input-number`, and related ticket controls

**`client/src/features/order-entry/OrderEntryForm.tsx`**

- Nested `ConfigProvider` `theme.components.Select` (`selectorBg`, `clearBg`, etc.)
- Symbol: `AutoComplete` with an `Input` child (not combobox-only)
- `Select` usage: `size="middle"`, `className="order-entry-ticket-select"`, full width where already wired (Side, Venue, advanced Order type / TIF)

## Exception

If the user explicitly requests adjusting or redesigning the order ticket UI, you may edit these files accordingly.
